abu bakr rabee ibn ahmad al-akhawyni bok.data-term: abu bakr rabee ibn ahmad al-akhawyni bokhari

examples.en: He stared morosely at the floor.
He became morose and withdrawn and would not talk to anyone.
examples.ru: Он стал угрюмым, замкнулся в себе, и не хотел ни с кем разговаривать.

examples.en: He fell morosely on the bed.
